# All About the Violin

The violin is a string instrument made of woood that usually comes in 3 sizes. 1/2 size, 3/4 size, and full size or 4/4 size. When your student is stil very young, you may be able to find smaller sizes, but these are the standard sizes that violin players use. The violin has 4 strings, the g-string, the d-string, the a-string, and the e-string, with the g-string being the lowest and the e-string being the highest.
